{"tid":1092672,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯5大聯賽入球超越C朗　而且比C朗少踢68場","createTime":"2019-04-05T04:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T13:29:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ebac05c11f9e9cd64f159471cf66ecde7084b605","tid":1092672,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"04月05日(五) 05:04   <br />\n<br />\n美斯上仗對維拉利爾攻入1球，協助巴塞逼和維拉利爾4比4，而呢粒入波亦令美斯超越C朗，成為5大聯賽第1射手。 <br />\n<br />\n近期C朗養傷，美斯在西甲就愈踢愈有，之前兩人同樣以414球並列5大聯賽射手王，而美斯上場再入波，暫時以1球超越C朗，獨享射手王美譽。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美斯嘅入球紀錄係446場入415球，比C朗嘅514場入414球成績更佳，因為美斯少踢68場</span>，而C朗短期內仲要養傷未能復出，美斯喺呢段時間有機會拉開紀錄。 <br />\n<br />\n不過C朗都唔係嘢少，等佢復出時，兩人新一輪鬥爭又會開始。"},{"pid":"c5194aa39d673726516b35ce198710353ea784bf","tid":1092672,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:48:38.000Z","msg":"係強隊點唔入波啊? 試下去中游隊睇下"},{"pid":"91f12a9a166b96727ca66c24aeb9cddba3e75135","tid":1092672,"uid":152230,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:51:11.000Z","msg":"其實巴塞真係咩位都頂級 好難比較"},{"pid":"d87700921745e5980487ddb2896d851e2cf48429","tid":1092672,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"拎到美洲盃冠軍先講"},{"pid":"24e52d7b99e0d2e0e83825b556bd99c7538bb0af","tid":1092672,"uid":4586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"alan"},{"pid":"84137357ae9df4c01b73d73e5ed6a86d98a429c0","tid":1092672,"uid":1426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"24e52d7b99e0d2e0e83825b556bd99c7538bb0af","tid":1092672,"uid":4586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"alan"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:55:18.000Z","msg":"alex"},{"pid":"d4fed1475ab816254d0cadec7a42bdece6f97b92","tid":1092672,"uid":17501,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"91f12a9a166b96727ca66c24aeb9cddba3e75135","tid":1092672,"uid":152230,"like":0,